node.text:
Week 3 is SUUUUPER late but here we go! üôÉ
•
Lately things have been extremely crazy and busy and I've spent a lot of time thinking about the changes that are headed my way. 
• •
Everyone has their own way of dealing with change but sometimes I lose sight of myself by over analyzing or stressing out about things I can't control.
• • •
I have to remind myself to focus on the positive and try to embrace the change; because I may not want it and I may not like it, but sometimes..it's inevitable. 
• • • • 
I don't ALWAYS hate change, but I won't lie; sometimes it just scares the crap out of me. 
• • • • • 
How do you handle change? Are you a boss who accepts it like a pro? Or is the struggle real!? 
.
.
